---

<section class="bg-primary-50 dark:bg-slate-800">
	<div class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-6xl h-screen">
		<div class="grid gap-6 row-gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="md:pb-6 md:pr-16">
				<h2 class="mb-8 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold font-heading">Timeline</h2>
				<div class="flex">
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
						<div>
							<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
								<span>
									<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">2019</p>
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
						<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">First line of code</p>

						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
							In my first university class, with no knowledege of programming, I wrote my first line of code in a
							mandatory Java unit. From there I was hooked.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex">
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
						<div>
							<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
								<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">2019</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
						<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">The web</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
							After admittedly spending too much time watching pointless tutorials, I began building sites. All done
							while studying my primary degree of mecahtronics engineering.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex">
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
						<div>
							<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2">
								<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">2020</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="w-px h-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="pt-1 pb-8">
						<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Production Time</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
							In 2020, I approached my old boss with the eagerness to work on the companies web app. From there, I have
							been maintaining the app till current date. To then rewrite the entire app with more modern technologies!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex">
					<div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
						<div>
							<div
								class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-primary-600 border-2 bg-primary-600"
							>
								<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-6 h-6 text-white dark:text-slate-200" />
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="pt-1">
						<p class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-slate-300">Today</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400"></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="mb-8 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold font-heading">Skills</h2>
				</div>
				<div>
					<strong>Skills Im Comfortable with</strong>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-1 items-center py-4">
						{comfortable.map((skill) => <SkillsItem item={skill} />)}
						<div></div>
					</div>
					<div>
						<strong>Skills Im Still Mastering</strong>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-1 items-center py-4">
							{mastering.map((skill) => <SkillsItem item={skill} />)}
							<div></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
